<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">Kunci skrin anda secara automatik</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<p class="p">Bila anda meninggalkan komputer anda, anda patut <span class="link"><a href="shell-exit.html#lock-screen" title="Kunci skrin">kunci skrin</a></span> untuk menghalang orang lain menggunakan dekstop anda dan mencapai fail anda tanpa keizinan. Anda masih boleh mendaftar masuk dan semua aplikasi anda kekal berjalan, tetapi anda perlu masukkan kata laluan supaya dapat menggunakan komputer anda semula. Anda juga boleh mengunci skrin secara manual, tetapi anda boleh mengunci skrin secara automatik.</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Click the <span class="em">system menu</span> <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/system-devices-panel.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="Power cog icon"></span></span> and
      select <span class="gui">System Settings</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Pilih <span class="gui">Kecerahan &amp; Kunci</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Make sure <span class="gui">Lock</span> is switched on, then select a timeout
    from the <span class="gui">Lock screen after</span> drop-down list. The screen will automatically lock after
    you have been inactive for this long. You can also select <span class="gui">Screen
    turns off</span> to lock the screen after the screen is automatically
    turned off, controlled with the <span class="gui">Turn screen off when inactive for</span> drop-down
    list above.</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
</div>
